### Pornhub Partnership Discussion
- [joaointech] mentioned an upcoming introduction to Pornhub founders via an insider.
- Potential partnership could significantly impact project growth.

### Automated Bot Link Issue
- [victory.sol] reported that the X link associated with the contract address (CA) on Photon was suspended.
- [joaointech] speculated it might be due to data pulled from pump.fun.
- [joaointech] committed to investigating if the link can be changed.

### DWTF Staking and Airdrop System
- [meltingsnow8210] explained the staking mechanics:
  - Stake NFT to earn $DWTF.
  - Stake $DWTF on GFM to earn $SOL and $DWTF.
  - Stake $DWTF on a custom platform to earn airdrops.
- Phase 1 of the staking platform launched.

### Green Dough and GFM Ecosystem
- [meltingsnow8210] highlighted Green Dough’s integration with GFM.
- It scans comments to detect scams/rugs.
- Jito SOL, Jup, and Meteora partnerships were mentioned as bullish indicators.

### EztrelaAI Product Evaluation
- [litn] tested EztrelaAI and confirmed it works but is not highly refined.
- Speculated potential market cap growth to 500K.

### Prometheus Meta and Market Trends
- [shooter.tradrai] noted increased interest in Prometheus-related tokens.
- [elvisgan] and [flygod0997] tracked price movements and speculated on future growth.

### Trust Score System
- Composite trust scores based on a social graph of trusted agents.
- Can be bootstrapped from existing Eliza trading system trust scores.
- AI16z tokens could be used, with a preference for agent registry & messaging over NFT-based implementation.

### Web3 Narrative Marketing Platform
- Uses Eliza OS Brain to generate and schedule content for multiple platforms (X, LinkedIn, Medium, Farcaster).
- Collects engagement stats and refines content strategy.
- Allows manual editing before posting.

### Open-Source AI Model Issues
- Released model lacks text heads, emotional detection, and Gemma-based components.
- TTS is high quality but slow due to inefficient processing (32 codebooks per forward pass).
- Community may optimize it for better real-time performance.

### Humanoid Robotics & Eliza Integration
- Interest in integrating Eliza AI into humanoid robotics.
- No concrete implementation details yet.

### Sith Show Runner in Unreal
- [godfreyart] inquired about running Sith Show Runner in Unreal.
- [smsithlord] suggested using an embedded web browser with a `postMessage` interface, allowing the engine to process events and set cameras while all TTS and show playback happen in the web tab.

### Show Playback Implementation
- [smsithlord] explained that playback involves stepping through a scene’s dialogue using TTS.
- A sample JSON from a show config and one episode is sufficient to understand the structure.

### AI-Generated Episodes
- Any AI, including local Eliza, can generate episodes as long as the output matches the required JSON format.

### Eliza Plugin & AI Performance
- [pendingreality] confirmed that the Eliza plugin is available on FAB and primarily interfaces with OpenAI or other APIs.
- Running a local AI model alongside Unreal may have performance issues.
